description: Returns the tags on an S3 Batch Operations job. To use the GetJobTagging operation, you must have permission to perform the s3:GetJobTagging action. For more information, see Controlling access and labeling jobs using tags in the Amazon S3 User Guide. Related actions include:

parameters.name: AccountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID associated with the S3 Batch Operations job.

parameters.name: JobId
parameters.description: The ID for the S3 Batch Operations job whose tags you want to retrieve.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: The set of tags associated with the S3 Batch Operations job.
